{"tid":1182850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳華為停手機生產線　 富士康相關人士傳出消息","createTime":"2019-06-02T13:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T13:10:38.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d147c9a70a32aba6f4199e214636fd4a012d06bf","tid":1182850,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/output-6-1-1280x719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Foutput-6-1-1280x719.png&h=c9d01317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《南華早報》引述富士康相關人員消息，指華為減少了新手機訂單，富士康已經停止華為手機的幾條生產線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據《南華早報》報道，華為旗下 Honor 榮耀手機全球總裁趙明在日前的最新發表會上，就華為是否仍然目標在 2020 年底前超越韓國三星，成為最大手機銷售商，趙明指「就目前最新形勢來說，要評論這個目標能否實現似乎是言之尚早」。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，《南華早報》亦轉述富士康有關人士的消息，指他們日前已停止了華為的幾條生產線，原因是華為對已減少了對手機的訂單。消息人士指，智能手機的生產計劃一般具有彈性，隨著環境變化可增可減，現時未清楚今次關閉生產線是短暫措施還是長期削減訂單。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/02/huaweifoxconn/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F02%2Fhuaweifoxconn%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=4b512123\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/02/huaweifoxconn/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"41e5b9f73e27564d8ab1a0f3d086ebbd066ad44a","tid":1182850,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"停部分定停晒先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb8c663eb46b82300bdcb82692560aed4d5d24f","tid":1182850,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"華為手機部門可以摺埋架啦<br />\n中共唔會犧牲任何野去救佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe320c6a3ee1b6329fc42c630ac59bb868c0dc8","tid":1182850,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdb8c663eb46b82300bdcb82692560aed4d5d24f","tid":1182850,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"華為手機部門可以摺埋架啦<br />\n中共唔會犧牲任何野去救佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}